{"tid":2094199,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳文敏：不應以保護國家安全為名　合理化專制統治","createTime":"2020-07-04T12:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T12:17:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3abdac10359ab69c126bc7c446beb6fd8ec66c30","tid":2094199,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:13:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535789-20200704.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535789-20200704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmndxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=661970eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535789-20200704.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=53181551\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535789-20200704.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院公法講座教授陳文敏認為，《港區國安法》涉及不少定義模糊的權力，令執法者有空間濫權，認為不應以保護國家安全為名，合理化專制統治或任意使用權力。<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏在港大法律學院一個論壇上，舉出《港區國安法》多條條文，指當中的定義含糊，有可能牴觸《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》，例如列明除非法官信納被告不會繼續危害國家安全，否則不得保釋。他質疑幾乎是有罪推定，而非無罪推定，認為不應利用還柙作為懲罰。而《港區國安法》內多項字眼，例如「國家機密」、「 國家安全」及「勾結外國勢力」均沒有清晰定義。<br />\n<br />\n陳文敏說，不明白為何唱歌、舉旗或叫口號可視作分裂國家，指《港區國安法》沒有明確訂明分裂國家的行為。如果示威者日後改用其他口號或字眼代替，甚至用白紙示威，當局是否亦要禁止。他說不會質疑保護國家安全的需要，認為政府贏得人民信任和尊重，正是國家安全的最佳保障，威嚇和鎮壓只會適得其反。"},{"pid":"9c6e1359c459d013d837ffa70343799fb91d656f","tid":2094199,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"前幾日佢明報專欄都要用曲筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7816d7b3b7f59a7bb259a9a65933f95baae9d25","tid":2094199,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:15:13.000Z","msg":"收聲la, 唔好激D白咭佬<br />\n又加辣"},{"pid":"e52feffab38df6a3204adf68959e64425b568dcf","tid":2094199,"uid":28432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T12:17:49.000Z","msg":"一句道出重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}